in root :

make pimpdradio.py executable : chmod +x /home/pi/pimpdradio.py
put link in /usr/sbin for startup : ln -s /home/pi/pimpdradio/pimpdradio.py /usr/sbin/pimpdradio

copy pimpdradio in /etc/init.d
make it executable : chmod +x /etc/init.d/pimpdradio
update system bootup : update-rc.d pimpdradio defaults
